							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "Views describe objects. They are implemented in methods of the class of the object, and are annotated with {{gtPragma:gtView}}. Views should document the intent. Examples can be combined with views to express narratives. Examples produce objects, views compress intent."
						},
