								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "Different objects can serialize themselves in different ways, and it's possibly in multiple ways at the same time. These are produced by methods annotated with {{gtPragma:gtLlmDataView}}. For example, an instance of BlElement will show both the slots and class and an image with the rendering of the element. Exploit each of these data views."
